26
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:26,880
Very good, Georgina, not just people, but also ideas,

27
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:30,960
religions, languages and diseases travelled from place to place

28
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,640
along these ancient roads.

29
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:35,439
